Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.19,0:01:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为在这个年纪\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I always thought by this point of my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是我给别人打恶作剧电话才对\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'd be the one making my crank calls.
