Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 这里是未来\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}My God. It's the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:03:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我的父母 我的同事 我的女朋友\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}My parents, my co-workers, my girlfriend.
