Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\shad3.75\bord1.875}3000年的船长\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Space Pilot 3000
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到明日世界\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Welcome to the world of tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你总是要这样说话\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Why do you always have say it that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你没听说过什么叫演技吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Haven't you ever heard of a little thing called showmanship?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 你的命运在等待你\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Come, your destiny awaits!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705,937.5)\fs105\1c&0x000000\3c0xC4FFFD\b1\bord7.5}命运分配部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:04:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你前途顺利\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Have a nice future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,酷 就像《星际迷航》一样\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Cool, just like in Star Trek. Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,下午好 先生\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Good afternoon, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,名字\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,弗莱\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我是丽拉\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'm Leela.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就要过年了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}It's New Year's Eve. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我只想尽快安排好你的命运 早点回家\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}so I'd like to decide your fate quickly and get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我能问个问题吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Can I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只要不是关于我的眼睛\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}as long as it's not about my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是关于我的眼睛吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Is it about my eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是的吧\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,问你的吧\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Just ask the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你的眼睛是怎么回事\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}What's with the eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个外星人 行了吧 现在换个话题吧\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'm an alien, all right? Let's drop the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,酷啊 外星人\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Cool! An alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你们占领了地球吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Has your race taken over the Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 我只是在这里工作\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}No, I just work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 那艘飞艇的时间准确吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Wait a minute. Is that blimp accurate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 现在是2999年12月31日\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Yep. It's December 31 st, 2999.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 一千年了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}My God! A million years!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定觉得挺难过的吧\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'm sure this must be upsetting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 应该是吧 但是\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You know, I guess it should be, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上 我很高兴\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}actually, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,过去已经没有什么值得我留恋的了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I had nothing to live for in my old life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我破产了 我有份很丢人的工作\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I was broke, I had a humiliating job. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,还有好像我的女朋友也劈腿了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}and I'm beginning to suspect my girlfriend might be cheating on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,至少 在这里你会受到应有的尊重\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Well at least here you'll be treated with dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 把衣服脱光躺到操作台上去\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Now strip naked and get on the probulator.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思 你的DNA检测表明\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Interesting. Your DNA test shows
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有一位活着的亲戚\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}one living relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他是你的曾曾曾…曾曾曾侄子\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}He's your great-great-great...great-great-nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 这个小家伙叫什么名字\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}That's great! What's the little guy's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,休伯特·法斯沃斯教授\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Professor Hubert Farnsworth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 我是整个未来最幸运的人\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You know, I'm the luckiest guy in the whole future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我获得了新生\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I've been given a second chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,而这次 我不会再做一个失败者\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}and this time I am not gonna be a total loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你的永久性职业安排\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Your permanent career assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,送货员\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Delivery boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不要再这样\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}No! Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,随便换一个都好\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Please! Anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的手拿开\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Take your hands off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人获得的工作都是他们最擅长的\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You've been assigned the job you're best at, just like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我拒绝呢\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}What if I refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:05:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你会被开…\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:05:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,随便\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,…开炮发射到太阳里去\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Out of a cannon into the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不喜欢做送货员\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}But I don't like being a delivery boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那没办法\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Well that's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很多人都不喜欢自己的工作\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}lots of people don't like their jobs,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但还是得继续工作\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}but we do them anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,人各有职 身不由己\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You gotta do what you gotta do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出手来\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Now, hold out your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我要给你植入职业芯片\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'm gonna implant your career chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,它会将你永久标记为送货员\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}It'll permanently label you as a delivery boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,把那个东西拿远点\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Keep that away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,站好别动 该死\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Hold still ! Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛分不清远近\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I don't have good depth perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,给你五秒钟时间放我出来\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You've got till I count to five to let me out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,一\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}One
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一千年后再见\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}See you in a thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1012.5,705)\1c&0x3336CA\3c&0x000000\b1\bord3.75}1000 年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1012.5,705)\1c&0x3336CA\3c&0x000000\b1\bord3.75}5 分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你欠我一次\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You owe me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,哇哦\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,无线电城变异馆\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Radio City Mutant Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,酷\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,城际快车\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Cross-town express?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,外地人\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Tourist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,电话亭 我可以打电话给侄子\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}A phone booth. I can call my nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,哇哦 一个货真价实的机器人\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Whoa! A real live robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不然就是某种劣质的新年装扮\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Or is that some kind of cheesy New Year's costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,来咬我闪亮的屁股\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Bite my shiny metal ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我看着一点都不亮\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}It doesn't look shiny to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,反正比你的亮 肉包子\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Shinier than yours, meat bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(472.5,675)\1c&0x27218B\3c&0x9B9B74\b1\bord3.75}自杀亭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 伙计 我有急事\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Listen, buddy, I'm in a hurry here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来个双人套餐好了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Let's try for a twofer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,请选择死法\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Please select mode of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"快速无痛" 还是 "迟缓剧痛"\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}"Quick and Painless" or "Slow and Horrible. "
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我想拨个对方付费的电话\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'd like to place a collect call.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,您已选择"迟缓剧痛"\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You have selected Slow and Horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,有眼光\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Good choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,放马过来吧 宝贝\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Bring it on, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 快点 赶紧杀了我吧\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Come on! Come on! Kill me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 我叫本德\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}By the way, my name's Bender.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,救命 这是怎么回事\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Help! What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,您已经死了 感谢使用"速死速绝"\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You are now dead. Thank you for using Stop and Drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,2008年以来美国最受欢迎的自杀亭\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}America 's favorite suicide booth since 2008.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没用的破铜烂铁\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Lousy, stinking rip-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天也没有什么别的安排\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Well, I didn't have anything else plan for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们去大醉一场吧\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Let's go get drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,二、三…嘿\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}two, three-- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到明日世界\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Welcome to the world of tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 泰瑞\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Shut up, Terry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这事没有商量的余地 丽拉\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}This is unacceptable, Leela.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:10:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须找到弗莱并植入芯片\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You must find Mr. Fry and install his chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说 他只是一个无名小卒\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Look, he is just a nobody
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是不想当送货员而已\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}who doesn't want to be a delivery boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得没必要强迫他\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'd really rather not to force it on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的工作 不管你喜不喜欢\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}That's your job, whether you like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我的工作就是命令你去做你的工作\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}It's my job to make you do your job,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不管我喜不喜欢\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}whether I like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这工作我很喜欢\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Which I do! Very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,现在快干活去\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Now get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,生活真美好\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Life is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,243.75)\1c&0xCBD1D8}D R I N K
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,机器人为什么需要喝酒呢\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Why would a robot need to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不需要喝酒\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I don't need to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我想戒的话随时都可以\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I can quit any time I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那么它们要逼你做送货员是吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}So they made you a delivery boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,哥们 那和我的工作一样烂\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Man, that's as bad as my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗 你是做什么的 本德\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Really? What do you do? Bender.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我是一个掰弯机\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'm a bender.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,掰弯钢梁 我的程序就是设定来干这个的\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I bend girders. That's all what I'm programmed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你很在行吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You any good at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,开玩笑 我可是业界明星\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You kidding? I was a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我能把钢梁掰成任意角度\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I could bend a girder to any angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,三十度 三十二度\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}30 degrees, 32 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,随便你说\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You name it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,三十一度\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}31
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.87,0:11:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不想继续活下去了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}But I couldn't go on living
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,自从我发现它们是用来做什么的\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}once I found out what the girders were for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么的\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,自杀亭\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Suicide booths.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,弗莱 很高兴认识你\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Fry, it was a pleasure meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我要自杀去了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'm gonna kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 你是我唯一的朋友了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Wait! You're the only friend I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的想和机器人做朋友\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You really want a robot for a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 从小就想\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Yeah, ever since I was six.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不希望别人以为我们是人机恋\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}but I don't want people thinking we're robosexuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,所以有人问起的话 就说你是我的调试员\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}So if anyone asks, you're my debugger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.09,0:11:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哦不 是那个独眼龙\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Oh, no. It's the cyclops.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,别看 别看\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Don't look! Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我没在看\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'm not looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,警察编号 1B-Dl\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}This is Officer 1B-Dl,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,请求支援\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}requesting backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们五分钟后赶到\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}We'll be there in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以躲在这里\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}We can hide in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这里星期二免费\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}It's free on Tuesdays!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到人头博物馆\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Welcome to the Head Museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我是伦纳德·尼莫\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'm Leonard Nimoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,斯波克\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Spock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,做这个手势\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Do the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经不能这么做了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I don't do that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真是难以置信\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}This is unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.22,0:12:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你们平时都做什么\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}What do you heads do all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们与人们分享经验和智慧\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}We share our wisdom with those who seek it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种体面的生活方式\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}It's a life of quiet dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,喂食时间\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Feeding time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉 但我必须给你安装芯片\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'm sorry, Fry, but I have to install your career chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你既然抱歉 为什么还要做呢\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Well, if you are sorry then why are you doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的工作\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}It's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,人各有职 身不由己\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You gotta do what you gotta do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.28,0:12:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,够了 你上了我的黑名单了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}That's it. You just made my list!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,停下 淘气包 坏总统\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Stop it! Down boy! Bad president!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 伙计 离那些头远一点\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}All right, buddy. Step away from the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我要让他尝尝24世纪的厉害\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'm gonna get 24th-century on his ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.01,0:13:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样 各位警官\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Please, officers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没有必要动用原力\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}There's no need to use force.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会处理的 怪女士\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Let us handle this, weirdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 他只是一个来自无知年代的可怜虫\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Come on. He's just a poor kid from the Stupid Ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的大鼻子挪开 独眼龙\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Keep your big nose out of this, Eyeball.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人敢取笑我的鼻子\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}No one makes fun of my nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你们刚刚完全失控了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You guys were totally out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我们的工作 我们是维和警察\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}That's our job. We're peace officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你也知道规定 "人各有职 身不由己"\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You know the law. "You gotta do what you gotta do. "
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 我们被困住了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Oh! We're trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,等一等 你不是掰弯机吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Wait a second ! You're a bender, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.33,0:14:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你掰弯铁栏我们就能逃出去了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}We can get out of here if you just bend the bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别做梦了 肉包子\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Dream on, skin-tube!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我的程序只允许我为建造工作而掰\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'm programmed to bend for constructive purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我看起来像一个逆掰弯机吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}What do I look like? A de-bender?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,谁管你的程序是编来干什么的\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Who cares what you are programmed for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有人给你编了跳楼的程序 你会照做吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}If someone programmed  you to jump off a bridge, would you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我得检查一下我的程序\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'll have to check my program.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,会的\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,开门\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 本德\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Come on, Bender.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,自己的生活自己做主\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}It's up to you to make your own decisions on life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是人和机器人与动物的区别\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}It separates people and robots from animals. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,还有机器动物\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}. . .and animal-robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你胡说八道 弗莱\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You're full of crap, Fry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你的话很有说服力 弗莱\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You make a persuasive argument, Fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,加油本德 你能做到的\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Come on, Bender! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 我做不到\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Can't. I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你是对的\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You were right, Fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,从现在起 我想掰就掰\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}From now on, I'm going to bend
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,无论任何东西 任何时间 还是任何人\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}what I want, when I want, who I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.51,0:15:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么能阻止我\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'm unstoppable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你是怎么做到的\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I don't know how you did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不了 谢谢\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我们当中必须有人掰弯这个栅栏\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Looks like one of us will have to bend this grate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Aw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(450,412.5)\frz22\bord0\1c&0x39496C}Fenusians\NNo home
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 这是什么\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Good Lord! What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这是旧纽约陷落的遗迹\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}It's the decaying ruins of old New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家 伙计\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Welcome home, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:15:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我住过的街区\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}It's my old neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 勾起了我不少回忆\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Man, this brings back a lot of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己记着好了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Keep them to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就是我和女友第一次约会的地方\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}This is where I brought my girlfriend on our very first date.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 她已经死了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}My God! She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识的 在乎的人全都死了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Everyone I ever knew or cared about is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿还有个你认识的人\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Wait, there's someone you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不能放过吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Can't you leave me alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经够悲惨的了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'm miserable enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这不能给你多少慰藉\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Look, I know it's not much consolation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我理解你的感受\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}but I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你不懂 我无家可归 没有家人\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}No you don't. I've got no home, no family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没有朋友\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}No friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我的世界已不复存在\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}My whole world is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你不可能了解如此孤单是什么感觉\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You can't possibly understand what it feels like to be so alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我了解\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我是这个星球上唯一的独眼人\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'm the only one-eyed alien on this whole planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我的父母从小就抛弃了我\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}My parents abandoned me here as a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至不知道它们来自哪个星系\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I don't even know what galaxy they were from.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道孤单是什么感觉\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I know how it feels to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,丽拉 我不了解这个世界\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Look Leela, I don't understand this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但很明显你了解\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}but you obviously do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我认命了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}So I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你真的认为我应该做一个送货员\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}If you really think I should be a delivery boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就做吧\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你的芯片\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Your chip!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,辞职\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.34,0:17:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我从始至终都想这么做\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Because I've always wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,直到遇到你 我才意识到这一点\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I just never realized it until I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你来凑什么热闹\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}What is the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想参与这个特别的时刻\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I wanted to be part of the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他偷了我的戒指\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Hey! He stole my ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 这下戒指消失之谜解开了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Well, that solves the mystery of the missing ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这值得干一杯\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}This calls for a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想破坏气氛\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I don't want to spoil the party,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在我们都成了弃业犯\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}but we're all job-deserters now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有工作也没地方可去\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}we are unemployed and nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,纠正：我们虽然没有工作\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Correction: we are unemployed. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:18:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们有个老亲戚可以投奔\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}but we have an old relative to mooch off of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好 我是迪克·克拉克的头\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Hello, I'm Dick Clark's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎收看3000年特别版\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Welcome to a special year 3000 edition of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,新年摇滚夜\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}New Year's Rockin' Eve!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你亲爱的老舅舅弗莱\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'm your dear old Uncle Fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有什么弗莱舅舅\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I don't have an Uncle Fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在有了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You do now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 我真的是你的侄子\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}By God, I am your nephew!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是太不可思议了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}This is absolutely incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能跟你要点钱吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Can we have some money?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 当然不行\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Oh, my, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,让我带你们参观一下\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Let me show you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的实验桌\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}That's my lab table and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的工作椅\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}this is my work stool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那边那个是我的跨星际飞船\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}And over there is my intergalactic spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这些是我收集的各种长度的导线\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}And here's where I keep assorted lengths of wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一艘真正的太空飞船\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}A real live spaceship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己设计的\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I designed it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还是来看看我收集的各种长度的导线吧\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Let me show you some of the different lengths of wire I used.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,注意了 各位弃业犯\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Attention, job-deserters!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,举起手走出来\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Come out with your hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你们已经被半包围了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}We have you partially surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住这些混混\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Get those bums.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们完蛋了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}We're boned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能用这艘飞船逃走吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Can't we get away in the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,从技术上讲是可行的\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I suppose it is technically possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我都已经穿上睡衣了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Though I am already in my pajamas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我带大家出去\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'll get us out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,有人懂得驾驶吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Can anyone drive stick?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我能\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,只要别让我侧方位停船就行\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}As long as I don't have to parallel park.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们胆敢起飞\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}If they try to take off,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就打得他们满屁股激光\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}give them an ass full of laser.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,准备升空\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Prepare for lift off!
