Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,发射\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Blast off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,开火 开火\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我看不清楚\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I can't see nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,景色倒是不错\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Pretty, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 没有了工作\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}So I guess without jobs
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得永远逃亡了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}we'll be fugitives forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那倒未必\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Not necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我想问问你们三个\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Are you three, by any chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有兴趣成为我的新船员呢\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}interested in becoming my new spaceship crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,新船员 你的老船员怎么了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}New crew? What happened to the old crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那些可怜老王八…但是\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Those poor sons of-- but
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那不重要\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}That's not important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的是 我需要新船员\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}What's important is I need a new crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有兴趣吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Anyone interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有 有\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:21:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这正是我梦寐以求的工作\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}That's exactly the job I've always wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你提供的职位 教授\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Thanks for the offer, professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们没有合适的职业芯片\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}but we don't have the proper career chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这不成问题\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}That won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,算你们走运\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}As luck would have it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我保留了旧船员的芯片\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I saved the chips from my previous crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是不是要在宇宙中穿梭\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Are we gonna flight through space
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对抗各种怪物 还有\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Fighting monsters and
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,教会外星女人如何去爱吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}teach alien women to love?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你的意思是运输货物的话\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}If by that you mean transporting cargo,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Then yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我为了赚点研究经费而发起的小生意\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}It's a little home business I started to fund my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.45,0:21:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,酷 我要做什么工作呢\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Cool! What's my job gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你要负责确保货物\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You'd be responsible for ensuring that
